iterations.yara_rule:
rule MalwareEvasionBypass
{
    meta:
        description = "Detects evasion bypass patterns in malware that exit early in sandbox environments."
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 53 FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // Push ebx followed by call to ExitProcess
        $pattern1 = { 50 FF 15 ?? ?? ?? ?? }  // Push eax followed by call to CloseHandle
        $pattern2 = { 33 C9 E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? } // XOR ecx, ecx followed by call to VM detection routine

    condition:
        any of them
}
